{"tid":950923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"尋日坐係天祐苑樓下喊 有個啊叔行埋黎...","createTime":"2018-12-22T02:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T12:13:33.000Z","uid":227795,"like":177,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"380a295016e24e2e03f42d851c6fa0c9463b14a0","tid":950923,"uid":227795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:16:39.000Z","msg":"佢同我講<br />\n<br />\n「啊妹 你唔好怪我多事 堅強d <br />\n唔好唔開心 知唔知啊!?」 <br />\n我含住眼淚 點一點頭 佢就行開咗<br />\n<br />\n佢走咗之後 我d眼淚即刻巴巴聲咁流出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喊到收唔到聲 喊到無力再喊先停<br />\n<br />\n因為做錯事想同朋友道歉 所以尋日係佢樓下等佢<br />\n等嘅同時 我諗起人生嘅缺失同困難太多<br />\n失去最好嘅朋友 睇住大家變做陌生人<br />\n個種無力感同後悔出哂黎 <br />\n令我就咁坐係到喊 甚至覺得做人有少少攰...<br />\n<br />\n但個一刻啊叔嘅安慰 雖然幫唔到我解決問題<br />\n但我真係覺得好warm同好感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想同佢講聲多謝<br />\n多謝你願意為一個陌生人打氣<br />\n多謝你令我覺得個刻我唔係自己一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以如果可以 無論識/唔識 關心多d身邊人<br />\n簡單嘅一句關心 有時已經足夠帶佢地離開深淵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n令佢地唔洗咁孤單同傷心"},{"pid":"b310668b0e0088c7cefe81fe32772084d5bf6e9a","tid":950923,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b01be3e04efa1061ef4fcc822021959d280e923f","tid":950923,"uid":192432,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:19:33.000Z","msg":"天祐苑我去過喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b5d38714b9a2cba734bbb2659ec0c253100f9cd","tid":950923,"uid":107364,"like":8,"dislike":33,"score":-25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:19:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2abe4084f8f5ed927727f1578bf3a0bd987b9b11","tid":950923,"uid":8441,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T02:21:50.000Z","msg":"偽娘<img sr